description: Kaffeine Coffee Co. relies on the shared passion and true love of Roasting, brewing and drinking coffee. Our Goal is to bring Third wave coffee to the Indianapolis Area. We plan to prepare coffee at the next level. From the high quality beans to the dozens of special brewing processes that Our customers may have never experienced. Plan to see us from Broad Ripple, Mass Avenue. and all cultural events around town.
name: Kaffeine Coffee Co.
